{"tid":456963,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"撚左幾下部iPhoneX,都幾肯定faceid之後兩年會係旗艦機標準。","createTime":"2017-11-03T11:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T08:44:02.000Z","uid":81397,"like":31,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"cc0628dcba101a276dbd6edeb337f7eb885a1f0f","tid":456963,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T11:32:12.000Z","msg":"問題係究竟An機要用幾耐先追得到？<br />\n<br />\n軟件問題<br />\n<br />\n因為Faceid軟件主力係AI，都係Google最擅長。而家應該落手搞左一排，調教到Android P果時係無可能出唔到。<br />\n<br />\n軟件問題不大，但都講緊下年IO之後既事。<br />\n<br />\n硬件問題<br />\n<br />\n反而硬件問題就嚴重好多，Apple同touchid果期一樣，根本而家臉部識別元件廠商係俾Apple包起左，如果落埋iPad Pro到或者好似傳聞講咁下年全部機種都轉用faceid ，An廠根本無得搭Apple順風車。<br />\n<br />\n要另外搵廠去研發／製造。呢個就會重複touchid果時個慘劇，兩年內無機到到Apple水準。<br />\n<br />\n總結：<br />\nQ1果期旗艦時間嚴重不足，可以放棄。Q3果期旗艦究竟做唔做到？"},{"pid":"f950875522cb41fc9cc1502d379f91fe6cbbf65f","tid":456963,"uid":20074,"like":92,"dislike":2,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T11:35:15.000Z","msg":"我唯一肯定就係三星一定加到同iphone x差不多價錢"},{"pid":"69c8989f83a2f890dd08d44027811c17979689a4","tid":456963,"uid":15835,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T11:37:37.000Z","msg":"其他廠其實都有<br />\n不過廢到無人用咋<br />\n成本最後又落返用家度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f270920eecf1a23139d1f7d2d0c6687e0121cd0","tid":456963,"uid":2933,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T11:37:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唯一肯定就係三星一定加到同iphone x差不多價錢</blockquote><br />\nNote 8 已經差唔多價錢啦唔係咩"},{"pid":"ba336f82fea74bcddfd71c3b66c3991be80e99ee","tid":456963,"uid":136002,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T11:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其他廠其實都有<br />\n不過廢到無人用咋<br />\n成本最後又落返用家度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n完全唔同技術<br />\n簡直係天與地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968460ca4814a3136f2dc