:1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:20:29.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得face Id加落新既mac更加必須"},{"pid":"c9d1f648f78a63509abc9fe33985c1950d5bf4fc","tid":456963,"uid":81397,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:21:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/430036/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/430036/page/1</a><br />\n我之前個POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2013年<br />\nApple推出Touchid，An俠：Touchid無用<br />\n<br />\n2014年<br />\n眾An廠於旗艦機上推出上世代滑動式指紋識別以圖追趕Apple，<br />\n但與Touchid相形見絀<br />\n<br />\n2015年<br />\n所有指紋識別成為Android標準，俾Ifan串android抄Apple時，<br />\nAn fan找出技術標準完全不同既上世代滑動式指紋識別MOTO機，試圖指出<br />\n<br />\n2016年<br />\n四年後，An廠終於追趕上Apple，甚至推出比Apple更快更準指紋識別<br />\n<br />\n2017年<br />\nApple推出Faceid取代Touchid，An俠：Faceid無用"},{"pid":"b019ae94513cb1771d7a5c33bde2159e7c5fb0cc","tid":456963,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:22:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而覺得face Id加落新既mac更加必須</blockquote><br />\n但MAC到今年先有touchid<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e54a15fe3bd5333c9691595754e2a986cec5a1","tid":456963,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:27:04.000Z","msg":"間間大廠有嘅patent都以千以萬計<br />\n何必話對方落後呢"},{"pid":"56fa8553d28b61e5ca426fdad5efc5c31312f097","tid":456963,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成本轉嫁消費者嘅情況下, 我暫時睇唔到用家俾多啲錢, 由指紋解鎖轉做面容解鎖, 用家得到乜野額外嘅好處。</blockquote><br />\n有手汗已經差好遠</blockquote><br />\n多撚餘 你不如講戴手套用唔到算啦 手汗都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有手汗咁普遍都唔撚講得??</blockquote><br />\n我就係有時有手汗解唔到果批人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講手汗有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都成日因為手汗要抹一抹隻手再解鎖</blockquote><br />\n唔好講手汗 核突啲有時liu完鼻屎用紙擦完都解唔到<br />\n我認真<br />\n<br />\n利申：出緊手汗"},{"pid":"33e96e0b08e051a35e98e94cdf782fa3857cf109","tid":456963,"uid":46231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:29:51.000Z","msg":"唔係face id 無用<br />\n係我覺得唔應該因為face id 而斬左touch id <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd54f24224893efa519473152b3d894959c18696","tid":456963,"uid":81397,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:32:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>間間大廠有嘅patent都以千以萬計<br />\n何必話對方落後呢</blockquote><br />\n其實係事實。<br />\n以三星為例<br />\n同時研究4個unlock方法，可以無一個做得好。<br />\ninscreen 指紋趕唔到，個planB係難以置信既差。<br />\n<br />\n而我都完全唔相信 inscreen touchid唔係Apple選項呢套說法，只不過faceid完成度夠高可以叫做彌補到缺陷。"},{"pid":"28522778f5958e34366eac7e9a2d57a5ead427eb","tid":456963,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:33:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係face id 無用<br />\n係我覺得唔應該因為face id 而斬左touch id <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估APPLE唔會加番咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9217436a96f751213e2552e2c6d9e5602c480ed3","tid":456963,"uid":6539,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係face id 無用<br />\n係我覺得唔應該因為face id 而斬左touch id <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估APPLE唔會加番咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正如mini jack一樣"},{"pid":"53fe1a68d5cf294a841d5a87593d2bcc2c4136af","tid":456963,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:37:38.000Z","msg":"有face id唔緊要，唔好取消touch id 嘛"},{"pid":"e2094baa31ab63ab93fbd7f2c5e37b6ef76d5261","tid":456963,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地蘋果出左faceid新技術又話冇touchid咁安全咁成熟，用翻touchid又話冇新意，一成不變，你地班香港人真係好撚矛盾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇返當年touchid一推出果時 班高登仔點樣話無用無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係笑死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3563608ed57c21f078f6c22ca2f9588daab7f84d","tid":456963,"uid":6539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:37:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係face id 無用<br />\n係我覺得唔應該因為face id 而斬左touch id <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估APPLE唔會加番咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正如mini jack一樣</blockquote><br />\n姐係佢講到faceid幾勁幾勁 我當下代佢技術上做到embedded touchid 但加返落去只係自打嘴巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2f4887a10e195a2af0ebc02c2de2646c62f73c","tid":456963,"uid":81397,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:38:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係face id 無用<br />\n係我覺得唔應該因為face id 