\n<br />\n而我都完全唔相信 inscreen touchid唔係Apple選項呢套說法，只不過faceid完成度夠高可以叫做彌補到缺陷。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三星係搞左咁多野竟然無個用於付款驗證<br />\n蘋果一步到位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0869c938e4e5fbed479f797ec85766734b8c518e","tid":456963,"uid":61210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:44:08.000Z","msg":"下年第一季/第二季魅族/MTK機都應該有類似faceid <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0eea50a059650cf2188a359050db06f36c7e0b0","tid":456963,"uid":6539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:44:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係face id 無用<br />\n係我覺得唔應該因為face id 而斬左touch id <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估APPLE唔會加番咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正如mini jack一樣</blockquote><br />\n姐係佢講到faceid幾勁幾勁 我當下代佢技術上做到embedded touchid 但加返落去只係自打嘴巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTIM COOK從來都唔介意自打嘴巴</blockquote><br />\n但以呢幾年作風我真係唔睇好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唯有希望r&amp;d落力整好個faceid 準備18年機<br />\n利申: 6s+開心使用中<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講起自打嘴巴就唸起pixel個發佈會 mini jack呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589c31488e9931d2a48306118f90908712e25c62","tid":456963,"uid":32121,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:44:38.000Z","msg":"呢代 Face ID 雖然唔係完全體，速度準成度寬容度都有待改善，但係在一般使用情況下已經非常好用。但係我覺得，幾年后如果屏幕底下嘅指紋辨認系統技術成熟，蘋果都有機會 Face ID Touch ID 並存係同一部電話之下，以彌補用家喺不同嘅情況下都可以解鎖電話，甚至乎喺某一啲需要非常安全的情況下，需要兩個系統共同使用以達致最佳的保安程度。"},{"pid":"7d2cc106236eb58