03T13:07:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得faceid 只係邁進&quot;真-無動作解鎖&quot;第一步<br />\n雖然touchid 撳實home 喺褲袋拎出嚟個feel 已經好接近<br />\n但係永遠都要有手指掂指定位置呢個步驟<br />\n<br />\n有玩過/睇過片都知faceid 解鎖速度好撚誇張<br />\napple 想將重心發展喺full remote control嘅話<br />\ntouch id 必須取代<br />\n<br />\n到時我就拎住部touchid macbook pro 喺度屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇過外國啲片，其實你拎緊出嚟時手指放定喺下面向上掃，就算你塊面未去到 face id detect 到個 angle range, iphone x 會收到你想去 home screen 嘅指示，當塊面一 detect 到就會去 home screen. 實制用時，同touchid 撳實home 喺褲袋拎出嚟個速度 已經好接近。<br />\n<br />\n某啲 case 係會仲快過Touch ID. <br />\n好似收到個 message 睇完想入 app 覆。<br />\n<br />\niPhone 8:<br />\nraise to wake, 睇到個 message, swipe 個 message 想直接入 app, prompt 你 Touch ID 解鎖，手指去認證，入 app<br />\n<br />\niPhone X：<br />\nraise to wake, 睇到個 message 同期已經解咗部機，swipe 個 message 想直接入 app, 己入"},{"pid":"420a1557313947dbaa1d23ebc41be946afc0f372","tid":456963,"uid":14078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:08:40.000Z","msg":"仲好似話a11有季習功能 faceid 用落會比初時快"},{"pid":"8dd9be78e2f83c22b47c69920f51a46f4c1a96bc","tid":456963,"uid":14078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:09:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲好似話a11有季習功能 faceid 用落會比初時快</blockquote><br />\n學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自膠"},{"pid":"2ff3399f1e4a1c486aa71ac35fcfb6c6d31f122c","tid":456963,"uid":38172,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:09:03.000Z","msg":"成班傻鳩 貼錢仲要免費送自己個樣俾蘋果大數據 話信美國佬安全果班仲好笑 你用蘋果機裝過大陸app,  用faceid技術一樣拎到你資料"},{"pid":"9bc0cfdaa90cdab49c8a12a8fa4b33019cc7e03e","tid":456963,"uid":46231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"我最想要嘅係嵌入式指紋解鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 直接撳落個mon到已經做到touch id 諗起都正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e1ac33de3ae02c57f75eb40f0a89dbcb736146","tid":456963,"uid":9964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco